---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Technical Expertise & Core Capabilities | Ranil Mukesh">
  <section class="container section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h1>Technical Expertise & Core Capabilities</h1>
      <p class="text-muted">Verified technical stack and architectural capabilities in Agentic AI and Machine Learning.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="expertise-grid">
      <!-- 1. AI Agents & Agentic Systems Architecture -->
      <div class="expertise-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="index">01</span>
          <h3>AI Agents & Agentic Systems Architecture</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="card-desc">Designing reliable orchestration and coordination layers for autonomous intelligence.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Agent design, orchestration, and coordination</li>
          <li>Multi-agent communication and decision-making frameworks</li>
          <li>Tool integration and autonomous action execution</li>
          <li>Human-in-the-loop agent systems</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Large Language Model Engineering -->
      <div class="expertise-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="index">02</span>
          <h3>Large Language Model Engineering</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="card-desc">Moving beyond prompts into deep model optimization and production-ready alignment.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Domain-specific fine-tuning for production systems</li>
          <li>RLAIF (Reinforcement Learning from AI Feedback) for safety and alignment</li>
          <li>Adversarial red-teaming for robustness validation</li>
          <li>Multi-modal LLM architectures (text, voice, image integration)</li>
          <li>Localization and cultural adaptation (Yazhi Tamil case study)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Production ML & MLOps -->
      <div class="expertise-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="index">03</span>
          <h3>Production ML & MLOps</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="card-desc">Architecting the infrastructure required to scale AI from research to enterprise deployment.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>End-to-end ML pipeline design and optimization</li>
          <li>Data engineering for model training and evaluation</li>
          <li>Bias detection, mitigation, and fairness metrics</li>
          <li>Deployment, monitoring, and continuous improvement</li>
          <li>Enterprise-grade compliance and security</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Data Science & Analytics Automation -->
      <div class="expertise-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="index">04</span>
          <h3>Data Science & Analytics Automation</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="card-desc">Decoupling insights from human bottlenecks through automated reasoning. (Referenced in SIRUS architecture)</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Automated ML model building and selection</li>
          <li>Database querying and natural language interfaces (Text2SQL)</li>
          <li>Insight generation and automated business intelligence</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. Localization & Multi-Market Deployment -->
      <div class="expertise-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="index">05</span>
          <h3>Localization & Multi-Market Deployment</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="card-desc">Adapting intelligence systems for cultural and linguistic nuances across global markets.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cultural and linguistic adaptation of AI systems</li>
          <li>Market-specific optimization for specialized demographics</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .expertise-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .expertise-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .expertise-card:nth-child(5) {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
  }

  .expertise-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.01) 0%, transparent 100%);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .expertise-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--text);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .expertise-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.01) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .index {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: monospace;
    padding-top: 0.4rem;
  }

  .expertise-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
    max-width: 20ch;
  }

  .card-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .expertise-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .expertise-card li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .expertise-card li::before {
    content: "â†’";
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
